|| 🎵 Nasheed Music Player ||

A simple and elegant web-based music player designed to play peaceful Islamic nasheeds. Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

|| 🚀 Features |

- 🎧 Play/Pause Nasheeds  
- ⏭️ Next/Previous Track  
- 📃 Dynamic Playlist  
- 🔊 Volume Control  
- 🕋 Clean and Islamic UI Theme  
- 📱 Responsive Design for mobile and desktop

|| 🛠️ Tech Stack ||

- HTML5  
- CSS3  
- JavaScript 

